descriptionHtml:
This is the bodyslide preset I made for my latest character FrejI wanted a more natural looking body, that would fit a warrior women.  Hence the smaller breasts, not much fat on her well trained body. But I wanted also too kep some femininity over her, hence why I gave her, thoes in my mind great hips and firm butt.   

If you want the body too look like my pics, you have too set the weight too 100 in Bodyslide, as it was there my focus on this preset was.

Plz upload pics of your characters using this preset if you want too :)

Enjoy
